═Hedged walls around a grassy space. A gap through the hedge to the right, another straight
across to the left. Two tree-stumps and a trunk in the middle.
Four overhanging trees and a brick chimney to the the left. 
Seven spaced railway sleepers straight in front.
Tall trees all around, in the distance the Abbey to the far left."█
